Authentication & Authorization

Authentication -> Is the process of identifying if the user who they claim they are.
taking an username and password and authenticating them to make sure the username and password is correct
is like loggin a user in

Authorization -> Determining if the user has right permission to perform the given operation.
makes sure that the user that send request to the server is the same user that actually logged in 
during authentication process. Its authorizing that this user has access to this particular system

JWT instead of using the cookies it uses a json web token to do the authorization

